adjectives.description: uncool (comparative uncooler or more uncool, superlative uncoolest or most uncool)

entries.meaning: (slang) Not in accord with the current fashion, standards or mores of a particular group; not cool.
examples: Synonyms: boring, dull, lame, pathetic, pitiful, sad, tacky, weak
Antonyms: cool, awesome; see also Thesaurus:excellent, Thesaurus:awesome
